The system makes use of heart beat sensor to find out the current heart beat level and display it on the LCD screen.
 The circuit also includes LED light and a buzzer which are used to alert the person supervising the heartbeat rate of the person and turns on the LED light and buzzer as soon as the heartbeat level of the person does not fall within the normal heart beat level set.
 
